author: gkossakowski
msg: Added context-path attributes for demo servlet declarations in order to avoid NPEs.

Currently we don't support empty context-path and we have no fallback mechanism for such situation. This means there will be NPEs as soon as the demo servlet starts to use getResource() method of ServletContext class) so it's quastionable if we should allow context-path to be optional at all.
